le=\"color: pink;\">侵犯人權的及損害香港自治的官員及人士的清單。名單裡的人在美國的資產可被凍結、個人和家庭成員的簽證可被撤銷，要求美國總統調查及制裁打壓香港自由的官員。會交代香港是否有官員因協助侵犯人權而需要受制裁。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">這有助國際社會持續監察香港的狀況，如能每年通過查證，實際上等同美國年年為一國兩制投下信任一票，這一方面有助有助保障香港高度自治，同時亦會加強國際社會對香港的信心。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DYm9M6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DYm9M6.png&h=40ab8a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LehviFs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLehviFs.png&h=cadff255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">未簽聯署即做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprgy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=a604622e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日12點遮打花園見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7A6LR0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7A6LR0y.png&h=81aa1e4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a4038c1a503fba059f097bcd8689eb6e8bad715","tid":1551680,"uid":153496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"冇足夠共識下就叫人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d01df4795d092e9dc80cf11365dc66558dd012","tid":1551680,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,